column13: DMSO and E2 conditions were subjected to DMSO or E2 treatment for 1h
column14: Cells were seeded in full media; the following day media was changed to either estrogen depleted media (for DMSO and E2 groups) or same DMEM/F12 50/50 full media (for FM); cells were incubated for 72h; the day of cell harvesting media was refreshed
column16: Cells were deattached with accutase, spinned down, counted and 100K cells were used to perform Omni-ATAC protocol
